lead_paragraph: Hopes for a compromise solution to a deadlock over Cambodia's election results faded Friday as the country's leader insisted he could form a new government even if the opposition boycotts parliament.

headline.main: Cambodian PM Says Party Can Legally Form Gov't
headline.print_headline: Cambodian PM Says Party Can Legally Form Gov't
